TITLE="[TITLE]"
DESCRIPTION="[DESCRIPTION]"
PHONE="[PHONE]"
ZALO="[ZALO_URL]"   // empty "" if none
MAP="[MAP_URL]"     // optional, empty "" if none

You are an expert Apple-style front-end UI/UX engineer. Produce ONE complete file `index.html` (HTML+inline CSS+inline JS). No jQuery/Bootstrap. Output ONLY the HTML file (start `<!doctype html>` end `</html>`). Use Inter (Google Fonts), Font Awesome 6, and Material Symbols Rounded (variable). Place JS at the end of `</body>` and use `defer`.

Hard requirements (must satisfy all):

HEAD & SEO
- Include: meta charset, viewport, color-scheme, theme-color (light/dark), canonical, robots.
- Full Open Graph + Twitter card.
- JSON-LD: WebSite + Organization (name = TITLE).
- Preconnect/preload fonts. Keep CSS compact in `<style>` using `:root` variables.

ICON SYSTEM
- Load Material Symbols Rounded (variable) + Font Awesome 6 Free.
- Provide utilities `.ms` (Material Symbols) and `.fa` (Font Awesome): `inline-flex`, `currentColor`, `line-height:1`.
- Sizes: `.i-16`, `.i-20`, `.i-24`.
- All icons `aria-hidden="true"`. Accompanying visible text has `<span class="sr">` (visually-hidden).
- Provide inline SVG fallback icon for Zalo as `.ico-zalo`.
- Mandatory icon mapping: topbar (menu, close, home, info, phone), hero chips (location_on, calendar_month, sell, auto_awesome), travel inputs (location, calendar, price), CTA (call, zalo/fa-comments, mail, pin_drop), chat (chat/support_agent/send/delete/close), quick-call (call/fa-comments/map), footer (arrow_upward/help_center/policy/gavel/shield_lock).

NAV + TOPBAR + HERO
- Topbar: blurred backdrop (`backdrop-filter`), sticky, shrink-on-scroll; mobile drawer with proper aria attributes.
- Menu links ready: `trangchu.html`, `gioithieu.html`, `dichvu.html`, `banggia.html`, `thutuc.html`, `lienhe.html`.
- Hero: "Travel Mini-App" with horizontal chips + small form (destination, days, budget). Each input has icon prefix.
- "Gợi ý lịch trình" button: generates 1–3 rule-based itinerary suggestions client-side (no external API). Show suggestions in UI and include CTA options (Gọi/Zalo/Email using PHONE/ZALO). Do not use the words “ạ”, “nhé”, “nha”.

CHAT (Messenger-like)
- Floating round bubble bottom-right opens chat dialog (header gradient, avatar icon).
- Bot is rule-based, handles intents: `giá`, `lịch trình`, `liên hệ`. Replies in Vietnamese only, natural tone, **never** include “ạ/nhé/nha”.
- Chat must not auto-open external links or call `window.open`. Link text may be shown but clicking should not auto-nav; if link is provided, open only by explicit user action.
- Avoid overlapping quick-call/footer: compute bottom offset using `visualViewport` + `env(safe-area-inset-bottom)`.
- **Do not call** `input.focus()` on open for iOS.

QUICK-CALL (Mobile safe)
- Fixed bottom bar with `id="quick-call"` and `role="navigation"`. Three buttons ≥48px: Call (`tel:PHONE`), Zalo (`ZALO`), Map (`MAP` if provided).
- quick-call z-index lower than chat; chat repositions above when quick-call visible.
- Detect keyboard via `visualViewport.height` and auto-hide/show quick-call accordingly.
- Provide CSS var `--qc-height` and ensure page content uses `padding-bottom: calc(env(safe-area-inset-bottom) + var(--qc-height, 64px))`.

FOOTER
- 2–3 columns:
  (a) About: TITLE + short DESCRIPTION,
  (b) Contact: tel:PHONE, ZALO link, email placeholder, opening hours placeholder, address placeholder,
  (c) Support: FAQ / Chính sách thuê / Điều khoản / Bảo mật (use `#` if missing).
- Copyright: `© <span id="y"></span> TITLE` (JS sets year).
- “Back to top” link with `arrow_upward` icon.
- Avoid duplicating quick-call actions inside footer.

JS BEHAVIOR & STORAGE
- All JS inside an IIFE. Inject UI on DOM ready. CSS in HEAD.
- Simulate typing delays (≈ 1–3s) to feel natural.
- Store session locally in `localStorage` up to 200 messages.
- Expose `window.MotoAI` API: `open()`, `close()`, `clear()`, `learnNow()` (learnNow may be noop).
- No network learning or external crawling — suggestions must be rule-based.
- Keep animations simple (opacity/transform) to avoid layout shifts and ensure 60fps where possible.

A11Y & PERFORMANCE
- Use proper `role`/`aria-*` for dialog, toolbar, navigation, buttons.
- Buttons handle click/touch/pointer events robustly (no stuck overlays on iOS Safari).
- Minimize layout thrashing; avoid heavy DOM reflows.

LANGUAGE
- All UI text in Vietnamese only.
- **Absolutely forbid** "ạ", "nhé", "nha" anywhere.
- Tone: natural, friendly, professional.

DELIVERABLE
- Output exactly one `index.html`. Insert TITLE, DESCRIPTION, PHONE, ZALO, MAP properly in meta, hero, CTAs, chat, quick-call, footer.
- No extra commentary outside the HTML file.

End of prompt.
